potential for Hands Free,

00:41:44.320 --> 00:41:47.160
and why it fits so naturally
into where McDonald's is headed

00:41:47.160 --> 00:41:48.850
as a company.

00:41:48.850 --> 00:41:51.710
So let me start by giving a
little bit of background around

00:41:51.710 --> 00:41:54.170
what digital means
to McDonald's.

00:41:54.170 --> 00:41:57.920
A lot of folks associate
McDonald's with convenience,

00:41:57.920 --> 00:42:00.120
and that is something
we want to perpetuate

00:42:00.120 --> 00:42:03.160
for a long, long time.

00:42:03.160 --> 00:42:06.240
Now, we believe that the
definition of convenience

00:42:06.240 --> 00:42:10.900
is changing, fueled by
technologies like mobile,

00:42:10.900 --> 00:42:15.440
and we think it's time to
introduce an entirely new level

00:42:15.440 --> 00:42:18.320
of convenience
for how people get

00:42:18.320 --> 00:42:20.770
their food on an everyday
basis, and that's

00:42:20.770 --> 00:42:22.550
what our focus is as a company.

00:42:22.550 --> 00:42:25.940
We're a provider
of every day food.

00:42:25.940 --> 00:42:28.650
So the possibilities for
McDonald's to use digital

00:42:28.650 --> 00:42:31.800
as a way to add convenience
are really endless.

00:42:31.800 --> 00:42:34.000
We invented the drive-through.

00:42:34.000 --> 00:42:36.300
I believe that mobile
will allow us to reinvent

00:42:36.300 --> 00:42:38.170
that drive-through experience.

00:42:38.170 --> 00:42:41.450
We're getting into the game
on delivery for mobile.

00:42:41.450 --> 00:42:44.840
And imagine being able to
come into the restaurant

00:42:44.840 --> 00:42:47.370
and skipping the line, taking
a seat, and having your food

00:42:47.370 --> 00:42:48.990
brought directly to you.

00:42:48.990 --> 00:42:51.110
That is something
we're already trying,

00:42:51.110 --> 00:42:53.490
and mobile is going to be
an important ingredient

00:42:53.490 --> 00:42:56.060
to that experience as well.

00:43:01.080 --> 00:43:04.250
Now, using McDonald's may seem
like a very simple experience,

00:43:04.250 --> 00:43:07.420
and in fact it is, but
there's a lot happening there

00:43:07.420 --> 00:43:09.990
when you unpack the
customer journey,

00:43:09.990 --> 00:43:15.020
and one of the key steps in
the customer journey is paying.

00:43:15.020 --> 00:43:18.330
So behind me what you can see is
Hands Free in action at a local

00:43:18.330 --> 00:43:19.710
McDonald's.

00:43:19.710 --> 00:43:22.220
We couldn't bring the restaurant
into the Moscone Center.

00:43:22.220 --> 00:43:25.680
They weren't cool with that
like the Coca Cola machine,

00:43:25.680 --> 00:43:30.670
so we had to package it
up in the form of a video.

00:43:30.670 --> 00:43:34.690
But as you can see, it's
really very, very simple.

00:43:34.690 --> 00:43:37.730
So how cool would it be to step
into a McDonald's and simply

00:43:37.730 --> 00:43:39.640
say, I'm here to
pay with Google.

00:43:39.640 --> 00:43:42.870
I think that'd be
really, really neat.

00:43:42.870 --> 00:43:46.960
So what you're going to be
able to do is no longer forage

00:43:46.960 --> 00:43:50.500
through your pocket or your
bag to pay at McDonald's.

00:43:50.500 --> 00:43:54.510
You simply arrive, convey
your order to the crew person,

00:43:54.510 --> 00:43:56.620
let them know that you
want to pay with Google,

00:43:56.620 --> 00:43:59.380
and Hands Free takes
care of the rest.

00:43:59.380 --> 00:44:02.070
The app helps us
verify that it's you,

00:44:02.070 --> 00:44:04.000
and we've integrated
our systems.

00:44:04.000 --> 00:44:07.550
So once Hands Free securely
charges your account,

00:44:07.550 --> 00:44:09.880
we give you your food
and you're on your way.

00:44:09.880 --> 00:44:13.370
It's really just that simple.

00:44:13.370 --> 00:44:15.760
So to quickly summarize,
we're big believers

00:44:15.760 --> 00:44:18.210
in the future of
frictionless commerce.

00:44:18.210 --> 00:44:22.470
We think that's coming to
the offline world at a very

00:44:22.470 --> 00:44:27.840
rapid pace, and we intend to use
that as an opportunity to add

00:44:27.840 --> 00:44:30.407
an entirely new level
to our experience.

00:44:30.407 --> 00:44:32.490
And it's for this reason
that we're really, really

00:44:32.490 --> 00:44:37.190
excited to team up with
Google on Hands Free.

00:44:37.190 --> 00:44:40.650
Suffice it to say we're really
excited to be a launch partner,

00:44:40.650 --> 00:44:44.760
and we're ready to co-create a
world that's just so radically

00:44:44.760 --> 00:44:47.510
simpler and more convenient
around how you get

00:44:47.510 --> 00:44:48.850
your food on an everyday basis.

